overview: Richard Dix stars as Dave Morrell, the new marshal of Goliath, Oklahoma. Immediately upon arrival, Morrell finds himself at odds with banker Coy Barrett (Victor Jory), who is actually the leader of all local criminal activities.
tagline: RITHLESS as the Outlaw's Code! DANGEROUS as a Loaded Gun! LAWLESS as the Untamed Wilderness!
title: Cherokee Strip
